{"tid":1941133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"GCE及IGCSE全球5月及6月考試取消","createTime":"2020-03-24T08:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T14:03:58.000Z","uid":305631,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4daa4e8ed61d989455d0926804ccdcff278db9a2","tid":1941133,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"考評局表示，負責GCE及IGCSE的主辦機構，宣布取消全球5月及6月的考試。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個主辦機構劍橋發聲明指，由於疫情迅速變化，全球多間學校均決定在5月及6月關閉校園，令考試難以舉行。而保障學生及老師的安全及健康是首要考慮，亦要確保學生之間的公平性，所以決定取消全球的考試，形容是一個艱難的決定。<br />\n<br />\n劍橋表示，學生將收到機構發出的評級及證書，之後會向學校提供有關如何向學生發出評級的指引。<br />\n<br />\nSource <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516509-20200324.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516509-20200324.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=c89f6267\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516509-20200324.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f21c59c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516509-20200324.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3c708acd0d98038b0ec91f69e741a8455c8306f5","tid":1941133,"uid":332772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T09:51:51.000Z","msg":"我依家讀緊asso 已經有conditional offer 但係要中文lv 3 or equivalent 因為我dse中文2左 所以本身報左今年考返igcse個中文嚟取代中文lv 3嘅condition 點知依家取消左igcse 有冇人知我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad818488f222fa313360d9e6e0df691cdf42ca5","tid":1941133,"uid":260350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c708acd0d98038b0ec91f69e741a8455c8306f5","tid":1941133,"uid":332772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T09:51:51.000Z","msg":"我依家讀緊asso 已經有conditional offer 但係要中文lv 3 or equivalent 因為我dse中文2左 所以本身報左今年考返igcse個中文嚟取代中文lv 3嘅condition 點知依家取消左igcse 有冇人知我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk